# E1: auto-generated platform icons from `cargo tauri icon`. These are build
# artifacts — tauri generates them every build from the source icon.png.
# We commit the source (icon.png/icon.icns) + the 4 paths in bundle.icon,
# AND icon.ico — tauri-build's Windows resource step requires it to exist
# at build time (it does NOT auto-generate it; only `cargo tauri icon` does),
# so CI checkouts without a committed icon.ico fail:
#   `icons/icon.ico` not found; required for generating a Windows Resource file
Square*.png
64x64.png
StoreLogo.png
android/
ios/